<p>[2]Gagné, M., &amp; Deci, E. L. (2005). Self‐determinationtheory and work motivation. Journal of Organizational behavior, 26(4),331-362. </p>
<p>[3]Fuhrmann, A., &amp; Kuhl, J. (1998).Maintaining a healthy diet: Effects of personality and self-reward versusself-punishment on commitment to and enactment of self-chosen and assignedgoals. Psychology and Health, 13(4), 651-686. </p>
<p>[4]平克龚怡屏. (2012). 驱动力 : Drive. 中国人民大学出版社. </p>
